If you sell online then use JennyClicks.com this plugin to increase & manage your sales!

This plugin allows you to track each & every sale plus run an instant commission affiliate program for your products. Just use a short code in your WP post or pages & you are good to go.

And best of all, everything is absolutely FREE! Just install this plugin to get started! For more details, visit http://www.jennyclicks.com
